comment:
* Holds all the relevant data needed to render a Smartspace card with the sub-image Ui Template. * * This template will add a sub-image card within the default-template card: *
    *
  • sub-image text1
      • *
    • sub-image text2
      • image (can be a GIF) * ...
    *
* * @hide

variables.name: mSubImageTexts
variables.comment: Texts are shown next to the image as a vertical list

variables.name: mSubImages
variables.comment: If multiple images are passed in, they will be rendered as GIF.

variables.name: mSubImageAction
variables.comment: Tap action for the sub-image secondary card.

methods.name: public List<Text> getSubImageTexts()
methods.comment: Returns the list of sub-image card's texts. Can be empty if not being set.

methods.name: public List<Icon> getSubImages()
methods.comment:
* Returns the list of sub-image card's image. It's a single-element list if it's a static
     * image, or a multi-elements list if it's a GIF.

methods.name: public TapAction getSubImageAction()
methods.comment: Returns the sub-image card's tap action.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel out, int flags)

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel out, int flags)
